      <title>债券交易员在四月份报告前收到不受欢迎的通胀暗示</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/treasuries-edge-higher-during-countdown-to-april-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，美国国债因消费者通胀预期上升而受到打击，因为交易员期待 4 月份有关价格压力的数据，这些数据可能会改变美联储货币政策的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/treasuries-edge-higher-during-countdown-to-april-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 14:24:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
